These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, indian, american, argentine, australian, german, canadian
1. the indian is in the middle##1
2. the indian is on the left of the american##1
3. the australian is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the colombian is on the right of the american##1
5. the canadian is on the far left##1
6. the german is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | australian | indian | american | colombian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  social-worker, chef, firefighter, security-guard, writer, dancer, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is on the left of the writer##1
4. the writer is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the security-guard is on the right of the dancer##1
6. the dressmaker is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | social-worker | writer | firefighter | dancer | security-guard | chef | dressmaker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, collecting, video-games, skydiving, baking, writing, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | baking | camping | writing | video-games | dancing | collecting | skydiving |

 #################################

 
