.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, epic, animation, zombie, comedy, action
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | mystery | fantasy | comedy | animation | action | epic |

